<h2>Where to go for a tourist</h2>
<hr />

<p>
    Welcome to the tourist guide! Here are some recommended places to visit:
</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Paris, France:</strong> The city of love, famous for the Eiffel Tower, museums, and its charming streets.</li>
    <li><strong>Tokyo, Japan:</strong> A historic city known for its temples, traditional tea houses, and beautiful cherry blossoms.</li>
    <li><strong>Rome, Italy:</strong> The eternal city, filled with ancient ruins like the Colosseum and the Roman Forum.</li>
    <li><strong>New York City, USA:</strong> The city that never sleeps, known for its iconic skyline, Broadway shows, and Central Park.</li>
    <li><strong>Bangkok, Thailand:</strong> A bustling metropolis famous for its temples, street food, and vibrant culture.</li>
</ul>

<p>
    Whether you're seeking history, culture, or adventure, these destinations offer something for everyone.
</p>
